SGX S&P CNX Nifty Index Futures Drop in Singapore Trading

-- B y   R e i n i e   B o o y s e n
-- 
2011-03-08T01:22:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-08/sgx-s-p-cnx-nifty-index-futures-drop-in-singapore-trading.html
SGX S&P CNX Nifty Index futures for
March delivery dropped 19.5 points, or 0.4 percent, to 5,463 at
9:19 a.m. in  Singapore  today.  The futures, derived from the 50 stocks on the underlying
S&P CNX Nifty Index on the National Stock Exchange of India Ltd.,
fell 1.2 percent to 5,482.5 in Singapore yesterday, and lost 1.1
percent in Mumbai to 5,475.60.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Darren Boey at 
 dboey@bloomberg.net  